{"tid":1260852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果掘磚就等於掟磚","createTime":"2019-06-27T03:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T04:01:41.000Z","uid":158996,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12792ad9c87f6cf07a90f43c7b1e27fc02a3399a","tid":1260852,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"咁灰衫 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警卧底</span> 就等於帶頭衝擊<br />\n<br />\n成日比啲廢老邏輯帶風向，今次仲唔到我地推爆你？<br />\n<br />\n發夢琴晚喺正門見住一個 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">灰色衫身形魁悟嘅勇武示威者手持棍狀物件衝上警察總部</span></span><br />\n我唔理前因係咩，我地好多企後排嘅人(包括記者)第一眼感覺係有人衝擊狗總，係鐵一般嘅事實。現場好多人唔知前因都即刻大叫佢落返嚟唔好衝。<br />\n<br />\n點知！最後警察開閘接佢入去！<br />\n<br />\n姐係點啊？！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係警察扮示威者帶頭衝擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我有理由懷疑：<br />\n612都係警察帶頭衝擊<br />\n磚係警察掟嘅<br />\n鐵枝係警察掟嘅<br />\n旺角騷亂都係警察從中作梗<br />\n火係警察放火嘅<br />\n<br />\n所有嘢都係警察嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自編自導自演</span></span><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB你仲要助紂為虐！遲早步ATV後塵！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推到上國際！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">越大阻力證明越有效！</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n警察好驚你地搞大「警察煽動暴動」呢單嘢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1260706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1260706</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d38643983ed4d90721b35aab1b9ce31ac0d78834","tid":1260852,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9a7e6e77be13a058d5c5b424b7ef0b625e9bb0f","tid":1260852,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f739e07ce979255890ab15bc088f68113808d836","tid":1260852,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}